@startuml
!pragma teoz true

title BeeGreen - Sequence Diagram: Control Flow for Sustainable Shopping

actor User
participant "Chrome Extension\n(Background Script)" as Background
participant "Chrome Extension\n(Content Script)" as ContentScript
participant "Chrome Extension\n(Popup)" as Popup
participant "Extension UI\n(SideTab/Dialog)" as ExtensionUI
participant "Store Page\n(Amazon/Instacart/Apple)" as Store
participant "Client Website\n(React App)" as Client
participant "LoopBack 4 Server\n(REST API)" as Server
participant "IBM Cloudant\nDatabase" as Database

== Extension Initialization ==
User -> Browser: Browse to e-commerce site
Browser -> Background: Tab update event
activate Background
Background -> Background: Listen for tab updates
Background -> ContentScript: Inject content script
activate ContentScript
ContentScript -> Store: Extract page information
Store --> ContentScript: Page DOM data
ContentScript -> ContentScript: Identify store type\n(storesCommon.js)
deactivate ContentScript
deactivate Background

== User Activates Extension ==
User -> Popup: Click extension icon
activate Popup
Popup -> Popup: Activate main logic
Popup -> ContentScript: Request cart data
activate ContentScript
ContentScript -> Store: Extract shopping cart info
Store --> ContentScript: Cart items data
ContentScript -> ContentScript: Analyze cart information\n(storesCommon.js)
ContentScript --> Popup: Cart data
deactivate ContentScript
Popup -> ExtensionUI: Display SideTab
activate ExtensionUI
deactivate Popup

== Product Sustainability Check ==
ExtensionUI -> Server: GET /api/products/{productId}
activate Server
Server -> Database: Query product data
activate Database
Database --> Server: Product information
deactivate Database
Server -> Server: Calculate sustainability score\n(dataprocessing)
Server --> ExtensionUI: Product with sustainability score
deactivate Server
ExtensionUI -> ExtensionUI: Display sustainability score
ExtensionUI -> User: Show sustainable alternatives

== User Contributes Review ==
User -> ExtensionUI: Submit product review/carbon score
activate ExtensionUI
ExtensionUI -> Server: POST /api/products/review
activate Server
Server -> Server: Normalize data\n(dataprocessing)
Server -> Database: Store review data
activate Database
Database --> Server: Confirmation
deactivate Database
Server --> ExtensionUI: Success response
deactivate Server
ExtensionUI -> User: Display confirmation
deactivate ExtensionUI

== User Accesses Client Website ==
User -> Client: Navigate to BeeGreen website
activate Client
Client -> Client: App.js routing
Client -> Client: Check login status\n(BeeGreen.js)

alt User Not Logged In
    Client -> User: Display Welcome page\n(Welcome.js)
    User -> Client: Login/Register
    Client -> Server: POST /api/users/login
    activate Server
    Server -> Database: Verify credentials
    activate Database
    Database --> Server: User data
    deactivate Database
    Server --> Client: Auth token + user info
    deactivate Server
end

alt User Logged In
    Client -> Server: GET /api/users/{userId}/dashboard
    activate Server
    Server -> Database: Query user purchases
    activate Database
    Database --> Server: Purchase history
    deactivate Database
    Server -> Database: Query sustainability metrics
    activate Database
    Database --> Server: Carbon savings data
    deactivate Database
    Server -> Server: Calculate comparisons\nand statistics
    Server --> Client: Dashboard data
    deactivate Server
    Client -> Client: Render Dashboard\n(DashBoard.js)
    Client -> User: Display shopping habits,\ncarbon savings, comparisons
end

== User Makes Purchase ==
User -> Store: Complete checkout
Store --> User: Purchase confirmation
User -> ExtensionUI: Confirm purchase tracking
activate ExtensionUI
ExtensionUI -> Server: POST /api/purchases
activate Server
Server -> Server: Process purchase data\n(dataprocessing)
Server -> Database: Store purchase record
activate Database
Database --> Server: Confirmation
deactivate Database
Server -> Database: Update user statistics
activate Database
Database --> Server: Updated stats
deactivate Database
Server --> ExtensionUI: Purchase recorded
deactivate Server
ExtensionUI -> User: Show impact summary
deactivate ExtensionUI

== User Contributes to Public Database ==
User -> Client: Navigate to Contribute page
Client -> Client: Render Contribute component\n(Contribute.js)
Client -> User: Display contribution form
User -> Client: Submit sustainability metrics
Client -> Server: POST /api/inventory-items
activate Server
Server -> Server: Validate and normalize data\n(dataprocessing)
Server -> Database: Store inventory item
activate Database
Database --> Server: Confirmation
deactivate Database
Server --> Client: Success response
deactivate Server
Client -> User: Display thank you message
deactivate Client

@enduml
